				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8122350/scp-4520#post-4378898</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2019 18:12:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Chris Kryzeth-Reyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5306787</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is almost everything I would have wanted from a dice-based SCP. Some kind of godlike or extradimensional being playing a tabletop rpg with our universe. And it even drops a bit of mystery into their origins! I love it, I only wish there were more of it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
