					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;Subject was instructed to observe an orange. SCP-4520 insisted that the fruit in question was an apple, before falling on his face and going temporarily blind. Subject regained sight approximately five minutes after this roll.&quot;</p> <p>+1, this is fantastic.<br /> By god, this needs a tale written for it.</p> 
				 	]]>
